== 製作 ==
2013年2月，[[照明娛樂|照明娛樂]]宣佈重製[[蘇斯博士|蘇斯博士]]的《{{link-en|鬼靈精 (小說)|How the Grinch Stole Christmas!|鬼靈精}}》<ref>{{cite news|last=Kit|first=Borys|title='How the Grinch Stole Christmas' Remake in the Works at Universal|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/how-grinch-stole-christmas-remake-419447|accessdate=2013-02-07|newspaper=The Hollywood Reporter|date=2013-02-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130209072150/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/how-grinch-stole-christmas-remake-419447|archive-date=2013-02-09|dead-url=no}}</ref>，並由[[班奈狄克·康柏拜區|班奈狄克·康柏拜區]]為主角鬼靈精配音。

== 發行 ==
電影原定於2017年11月10日上映<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/universal-dates-despicable-me-3-671303 |title=Universal Dates 'Despicable Me 3,' New 'Grinch Who Stole Christmas' |publisher=The Hollywood Reporter |date=2011-11-17 |accessdate=2014-01-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140118002827/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/universal-dates-despicable-me-3-671303 |archive-date=2014-01-18 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，後延期到2018年11月9日上映<ref>{{cite news|last=Kroll|first=Justin|url=http://variety.com/2016/film/news/grinch-remake-release-delayed-2018-1201790869/|title=Illumination's ‘The Grinch’ Pushed Back to 2018|publisher=Variety|date=2016-06-07|accessdate=2016-06-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160608131105/http://variety.com/2016/film/news/grinch-remake-release-delayed-2018-1201790869/|archive-date=2016-06-08|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 評價 ===
[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]根據180條評論，持有59%的新鮮度，平均得分5.95／10<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_grinch|title=The Grinch (2018)|work=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]]|publisher=[[Fandango_Media|Fandango Media]]|accessdate=2018-12-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181115142011/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_grinch/|archive-date=2018-12-23|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]上，電影獲得了51分<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.metacritic.com/movie/the-grinch|title=The Grinch reviews|website=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]|accessdate=2018-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181108060834/https://www.metacritic.com/movie/the-grinch|archive-date=2018-11-08|dead-url=no}}</ref>。據[[CinemaScore|CinemaScore]]調查，觀眾的評價在A+至F落於「A-」<ref name="opening" />。

